132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jon Tetzlaff/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction &amp; Thesis</h2> <p>TFI International (NY: <span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TFII\" title=\"TFI International Inc.\">TFII</a></span> &amp; TSX:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TFII:CA\" class=\"ticker-link\">TFII:CA</a>) is a large North American logistics and transport company with a diversified portfolio of business spanning truckload (TL), less-than-truckload (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LTL\" title=\"ProShares Trust - ProShares Ultra Telecommunications\">LTL</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148550106/image_2148550106.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745701-tfi-international-monitor-before-pulling-the-trigger", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 01:28:57", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745699", "title": "Buy The Dip: High-Yield High-Growth Stocks Getting Way Too Cheap", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money Saving Graph\" data-id=\"2158301126\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Federal Reserve's announcement that they anticipate fewer rate cuts moving forward than previously projected in their dot plot has sent markets into a panic. This recent drop only accelerated the pullbacks already being experienced by several high-yield, high-growth stocks that appear</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2158301126/image_2158301126.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745699-buy-the-dip-high-yield-high-growth-stocks-getting-way-too-cheap", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 01:14:40", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745697", "title": "URNJ: A Great Value Opportunity", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Nuclear power station\" data-id=\"182860157\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/image_182860157.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/182860157/i